---
title: logistics-agent 应用架构图
---
flowchart TD
  classDef actor fill:#F6F0E1,stroke:#8A6B3D,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#2F2415
  classDef app fill:#EAF3FB,stroke:#3C6E99,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#17324D
  classDef core fill:#EAF7EE,stroke:#4C8E64,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#14361F
  classDef infra fill:#FFF3E2,stroke:#B56A00,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#4D2C00
  classDef note fill:#F7F7F7,stroke:#7C7C7C,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray:4 3,color:#333333

  request[用户发起客服诉求]:::actor --> api

  subgraph agent[logistics-agent 应用]
    direction TB
    api[REST API<br>/api/v1/agent/chat<br>8081]:::app --> controller[AgentController]:::app
    controller --> service[AgentService]:::core
    service --> chat[Spring AI ChatClient]:::core
    chat --> reply[生成自然语言答复]:::actor
  end

  prompt[System Prompt<br>约束三类失败语义的回复策略]:::note
  prompt -.约束回复策略.-> chat

  subgraph abilities[能力层]
    direction TB
    model[大模型能力<br>通义千问<br>DashScope OpenAI 兼容接口]:::infra
    mcp[MCP 工具能力<br>MCP Client 自动注册远程工具<br>为 ToolCallback]:::infra
  end

  chat --> model
  chat --> mcp
  reply --> response[返回给用户]:::actor